{"tid":1034173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局據報將發 6 虛擬銀行牌照　中資佔 4 席","createTime":"2019-02-23T16:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T13:53:29.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"18629f4e6604706e8c77ccd658a39047cd5c250c","tid":1034173,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:46:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/finance/港虛擬銀行據報將發-6-牌照-中資佔-4-席-螞蟻金服-小米有份/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%87%E7%99%BC-6-%E7%89%8C%E7%85%A7-%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E4%BD%94-4-%E5%B8%AD-%E8%9E%9E%E8%9F%BB%E9%87%91%E6%9C%8D-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BD%2F&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xY%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=986327ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%99%9B%E6%93%AC%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%87%E7%99%BC-6-%E7%89%8C%E7%85%A7-%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E4%BD%94-4-%E5%B8%AD-%E8%9E%9E%E8%9F%BB%E9%87%91%E6%9C%8D-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%BD%2F&h=f58c3ee0\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/finance/港虛擬銀行據報將發-6-牌照-中資佔-4-席-螞蟻金服-小米有份/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/bank3-01_vpHmU_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fbank3-01_vpHmU_1200x0.png&h=7ab3ce82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金管局即將發出虛擬銀行牌照，料衝擊傳統金融零售業務。《金融時報》引述不具名消息人士報道，香港數週內將批出首批虛擬銀行牌照，六個財團將獲得牌照，四個為中資，分別為阿里巴巴旗下螞蟻金服、騰訊（700）財付通、小米（1810）、眾安（6060）夥中信銀行（998）的財團，渣打（2888）及香港電訊（6823）。<br />\n<br />\n金管局：爭取3月底發牌　篩選8申請者最後盡職審查<br />\n<br />\n金管局接受《立場》查詢，會爭取在3月底之前可以開始發虛擬銀行牌照，目前不會公布申請機構名單。金管局提到，已在大約20份已提交接近完備資料的申請中，篩選了八份作最後的盡職審查，八份申請來自不同背景，包括本地、内地和海外公司，當中包括銀行、非銀行金融機構和科技公司，目前處理申請的進度良好。"},{"pid":"367fa0575a574ad8a095a7548bd4ec7c2f155226","tid":1034173,"uid":65300,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:51:18.000Z","msg":"大陸又吸水  睇路"},{"pid":"91638cdbba39fe1f2739830977c2796a4176aca4","tid":1034173,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:57:08.000Z","msg":"不如香港人搞個虛擬政府算啦"},{"pid":"dd3f56c51ff895a08cff5bd05622dc1810a5ee8c","tid":1034173,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:57:31.000Z","msg":"螞蟻金服應該最大威脅"},{"pid":"efe38be6f31567e935eb2cd944f5bb6b44f8a817","tid":1034173,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"即係得2間揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}